# ===== Data folder — default-deny (Pattern B) =====
# Everything inside data/ is ignored, except curated INPUTS that the
# pipeline needs to run. This prevents accidental commits of large
# generated outputs (videos, DB, synthesis JSONs, model artifacts).
#
# To track a new input folder, add another `!data/<name>/` line below.
data/*

# Allowlisted inputs (small, curated, required by the pipeline)
!data/cricsheet/
!data/espncricinfo/
!data/player_aliases.yaml

